{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Uhdens Traukâ\npeetruhke / tad nomette ta to\nBehrnu appakſch weenu Kruhmî.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un nogahje/ un apſehdahs\ntur pretti / Bultas Schahwena\nTahkumâ/jo tafazzija: es ne war-\nru redſeht to Behrnu nomirstam/\nun apſehdahs tur pretti/un pazeh-\nle ſawu Balfi / un raundaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un DEews klanfija ta\nPuischa Balfi/ un tas DEewa\nEngelis fauze Ahgari no Deb-\nbes / un fazzija us to : Kas tew\nfait / Ahgare ? ne bihſtees / jo\nDEews irr ta Puischa Balfi\nklanfijis / tai Weetâ / kur wiꞥſch\nirr/ zellees/ pazell to Puifi / un\nturri to ſtipri pee tawas Rohkas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo es zelschu winnu par\nweenu leelu Tautu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un DEews atwehre win-\nnas Azzis/ un ta eernudfija wee-\nnu Uhdens Akku / un gahje un\npildija to Trauku ar Uhdeni / un\ndsirdinaja to Puifi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un DEews bija ar to Puifi/\nun tas auge/ un dſihwoju Tuḱneſti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tappe Strehsneeks ar\nStohpu / un dſihwoja Waranas\nTuḱneſti / un winna Mahte neh-\nme tain weenu Seewu/ no Egip-\ntes-Semnes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tanni Laikâ runnaja\nAbimeleks un Pihkols winna\nKaxra-Spehka Wirſneeks ar Ah-\nbrâimu/ fazzidami : DEews irr\nar tew wiſſas Leetâs/ ko tu darri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nu fwehre man tchet-\ntan pee Deewa / ka tu ne gribbi\nwiltigs buht prett mann/ jeb prett\nmanneem Behrneem/ nedg prett\nmanneem Behrnu-Behrneem/\npehz tahs Schehlastibas / ko es\npee tew darrijs / buhs tew pee\nman darriht/ un pee tahs Sem-\nmes / kurrâ tu weens Sweschi-\nneeks bijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbrâims fazzija:\nEs gribbu fwehreht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbrâims norahje to\nAbimeleku / weenas Uhdens Ak-\nkas deht/ ko Abimeleka Kalpi ar\nWarru bij rehmutchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Abimeleks:\nEs ne efmu finnajis/ kas fcho Lee-\ntu irr darrijs / ir tu man to ne\neffi pafazzijis / un es to ar ne ef-\nimu dsirdejis lihds fchodeen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbraims nehme A-\nwis/ un Wehrſchus / un dewe\ntohs Abimelekam/ un tee darrija\nabbee weenu Derribu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Ahbrâims likke feptiu\nJehrus no Awini fewischki.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Abimeleks ue\nAhbrâimu: Par fo irr ſchee feptiu\nJehri ? ko tu fewischki effi lizzis\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija : Pa-\nto / ka tew tohs feptiu Jehrus\nno mannas Rohkas buhs nemt\nka tas man par Leezibu effus/ fo\nes fcho Akku razzis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz tappe ta Weet-\nnoſaukta Bersaba / ka tee abbe-\ntur bij fwehrejschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad darrija tee weenu\nDerribu Bersgbâ / pehz to zeh-\nlah\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
